This pendant is stunning. 

Are you a lover of the open road, motorcycling with your friends and family? Do you enjoy wearing motorcycle jewelry to show your passion for it? Do you love to give gifts that reflect the personality, hobby or lifestyle of your favorite people? 

This handcrafted motorcycle necklace sounds like the perfect gift to get for yourself or someone you love! The motorcycle is antique silver-plated pewter, which is more durable and tarnish-resistant than silver. The stainless steel chain is available in many different styles and lengths so you choose your personal preference, and it is strong, won’t tarnish or rust, and won’t leave you with a green ring around your neck! If you’re looking for a fabulous gift for your favorite biker, this is something that will show your thoughtfulness and consideration of his or her favorite activities.  We even send you a gift box with a ribbon already attached, so all you have to do is give your gift and get ready for the thrilled reaction!

I just love it and was thrilled how it turned out.  The washer is gold toned stainless steel and laser engraved in black ink with the words:  Live Love Bike

The motorcycle is made of silver plated pewter (nickel and lead free).  The jump ring which holds the motorcycle in place is also made of stainless steel.  

This is a sturdy, strong piece that should last a lifetime!

Please see the second and third pictures for our new packaging! We are so excited about our new gift envelope and the sticker that reads "Handmade With Love, Especially for You"! That says it all! You cared enough to have something made especially for a loved one (or yourself)!

results.title: Thank You for Sharing in your Special Day- Rustic Style Sign for Special day We personalize at bottom with names- Weddings/Special Occassion
results.description:
"Thank You for Sharing in our Special Day" Sign for your Rustic Wedding. This sign is a great start for the wedding or reception and shows appreciation to those sharing in your special day. You can have it placed on an easel for guests as they sign in or easily attach a 1x3 to put it in the ground for guests to see as they are coming or going.

This sign measures approximately 7.25 x 12 inches and is on 3/4 inch wood. Signs are shown in Gray/Antique White and Black/Antique White
We offer several different signs in our shop, so be sure to check our Wedding section, so you get the one that is the perfect fit for you. 

• Shipment is generally 3 to 5 business days.

• Hanger attached on backside for easy hanging

• Several other color options available in drop down selection. The first color will be the color of the text & second color will be the background.

• Hand painted laser engraved creation is made to order.

• If we are shipping directly as gift, we can enclose a small handwritten note card, be sure to let us know what you want the card to say in the NOTES section when you order.

• For PERSONALIZED signs or signs you want modified please put the information in the NOTES section when you place your order.

• PROCESS Our handcrafted creations are made using a 7 step process to create a beautiful expression to be cherished for years to come. Two contrasting colors of paint are applied, the design is laser engraved, a fine hairline is applied to the design which gives an awesome touch. The final touches are completed once it goes through our antiquing process with edges distressed.

• COLOR We have a variety of color choices, but if you don't see what you are looking for, please ask  & we will see if we can make it happen for you. Keep in mind when selecting the color options, the first color is the text color, while the second color is the background. See policies for additional questions/clarification on colors.

• Please note these signs are not massed produced but each is unique and no two are exactly the same.

• When working with wood and the antiquing process, each sign has its own warmth and charm. While we try to get the best wood at the lumber yard, sometimes there will be knots or other slight imperfections in the wood, this is considered adding character to the rustic style of this line of our signs. Thanks for stopping by our shop and please do not hesitate to ask any questions.
